CHIP HOPE CO LTD (8084)  said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 21.27% to NT$210,039,000 from NT$266,790,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            210,039          266,790    
YOY%             -21.27%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            728,583          964,602    
YOY%             -24.47% 
=================================================================
 